    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041074005",
    "title": "初夏、日差しは燦々と",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "初夏の日差しがまばゆい昼下がりのこと。\r\n終業のチャイムが鳴った頃、トレーナー室の扉が開いた。",
            "enText": "It was a dazzling afternoon in the early summer sun. \nThe door to the trainer's office opened just as the \nchime of the end of the school day sounded.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "pathId": 2804406524377664211,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさま。\r\n今、少々よろしいでしょうか～？",
            "enText": "Dear Trainer. May I have a moment now?",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 167,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 498118980054277171
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 27,
                    "pathId": 6608429757362475898
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3707620321687240210,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "入ってきたのは担当ウマ娘、メジロブライトだった。\r\nしかし彼女は今日、実家関連の用事があるとかで――",
            "enText": "Entering the room was the horsegirl in charge, Mejiro Bright. But \nshe had something to do today related to her parents' home.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "トレーニングは休みじゃなかった？",
                    "enText": "I thought training was off?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 151,
                    "pathId": -8732129343621616438
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5384498467858631821,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "ええ。今はご用事のためにお屋敷からお車が、\r\nぶ～んとお迎えに来るのを待っているところなのですが。",
            "enText": "Yes. I'm just waiting for a car to pick \nme up from the mansion for my business.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 332,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 260,
                    "pathId": 1708779559580278270
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": 8869341853328170984
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1229383401598155957,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "ですから～、お迎えの時間まで、\r\nここで待たせていただいてもよろしくて？",
            "enText": "So, I'm happy to wait here until it's time to pick you up.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 193,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ああ、もちろん！",
                    "enText": "Yes, of course!",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "うん、もちろん！",
                    "enText": "Yes, of course!",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 131,
                    "pathId": -1102230406034021048
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -5246803754154472871
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2814750833484135318,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "ありがとうございます。\r\nではでは……しばらく、お邪魔させていただきますわ～。",
            "enText": "Thank you very much. I'll see you…… for a while!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 299,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 184,
                    "pathId": -4764649418375054582
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": -1442818518145549139
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4525933109990846662,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "もうすっかり夏ですわね～。\r\n今度のお休みは、きっと絶好の遊園地日和になりますわ。",
            "enText": "It's already summer! Your upcoming vacation will surely be a \nperfect day to visit the amusement park.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 307,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "遊園地日和？",
                    "enText": "Amusement park day?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": 6904126450031371224
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 35,
                    "pathId": -1139894896067272284
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6616464356618564862,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "はい～。この間、\r\nお父さまがチケットを送ってくださって――",
            "enText": "Yes～. Your father sent me a ticket the other day.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 213,
            "pathId": 6008922760844543117,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "しばらく、とりとめのない話をする。\r\nゆったりと流れる時間が心地よいが――",
            "enText": "For a while, we talk about nothing more than what we can't talk \nabout. Time passes leisurely, but it's pleasant.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "なかなか迎えが来ないな……",
                    "enText": "It's not easy to get picked up. ……",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "なかなか迎えが来ないね……",
                    "enText": "It's not easy to get picked up. ……",
                    "nextBlock": 10
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": -4032861690113206566
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7787925451808291149,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "そうですわね～……でも、のんびりするのは得意ですし。\r\nもう少し待ってみようと思いますの。",
            "enText": "You're right -…… but I'm good at taking it easy. I think I'll \nwait a little longer.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 334,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 195,
                    "pathId": -6688494223076830261
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": -7745411735153825013
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7838005686124844257,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "あ、けれど、トレーナーさまは『早上がり』のできる日ですわよね？\r\nもうこちらのお部屋からは出てゆかれますか～？",
            "enText": "Oh, but it's an \"early bird\" day for the trainer, isn't it? Will \nyou be leaving this room now?",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 331,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": -1962982303653096009
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": 9033434630979143272
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8659156013455406085,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "確かに練習の予定がない今日は、普段より早く帰れる日だった。\r\nしかし、メジロブライトを放り出すわけにもいかないだろう。",
            "enText": "Indeed, with no practice scheduled, today was the \nday to go home earlier than usual. However, I would \nnot be able to throw out the Mejiro Bright.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "大丈夫。まだここにいるから",
                    "enText": "It's okay. I'm still here.",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": -2534798338721888828
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7712929817366992412,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "ありがとうございます。\r\n……ふふ、なんだか思い出しますわ～。",
            "enText": "Thank you, I will try to find it.…… Hmmm… I kind of remember that!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 220,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 103,
                    "pathId": 4793603443135412249
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 6719393891824567803
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1634273598236684535,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "こうして2人で並んで、の～んびりしていたこと。\r\n冬の頃にもありましたわね～……。",
            "enText": "We used to stand side by side like this and \nrelax. It happened in the winter too～ ……",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 248,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": 6785260738286839244
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 32,
                    "pathId": -1543996421510849841
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4493641345684761134,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "……トレーナーさまが、隣にいてくださると……\r\nわたくし、いつもより――",
            "enText": "When…… the trainer is next to me…… I am always more―",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 233,
            "pathId": 1593358869676244519,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "もっと、のんびりさんになってしまうような気が\r\nいたしますのよ……。",
            "enText": "I feel like I'd be more of a laid-back person. ……",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 200,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 239,
                    "pathId": 6566717774180633392
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": 7628856097149620576
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6337763826483808884,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "（キーンコーン……カーンコーン……）",
            "enText": "(keencorn…… kerncorn ……)",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -5173153462289462558
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": 3474779265384969973
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5430248192095224386,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "……あら～？\r\nまあ、まあ……もう、すっかり夕暮れ時なのですね～？",
            "enText": "…… Oh, dear? Well, well, well.…… It's already dusk, isn't it～?",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 302,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "……やっぱり、迎えが遅いよな？",
                    "enText": "…… I knew it was too late to pick you up, right?",
                    "nextBlock": 19
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "……やっぱり、迎えが遅いよね？",
                    "enText": "…… I knew it was too late to pick you up, right?",
                    "nextBlock": 19
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 159,
                    "pathId": 794041994779032870
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 42,
                    "pathId": -3369080634965856175
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6908704374458053270,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『早上がり』の予定はどこへやら。\r\n時計は残業もあわやという時間を示している。",
            "enText": "Where is my \"early bird\" schedule? The clock is showing that it \nis almost time for me to work overtime.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 134,
                    "pathId": 7052270666757881750
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3645932702797768718,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "確かに、メジロ家の運転手さまが\r\nわたくしよりのんびりなさっているのは珍しいことですわ。",
            "enText": "Indeed, it is rare that the driver of the Mejiro family is more \nlaid back than I am.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 284,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": -806211985156971062
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5183908348781751377
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6179966212651135278,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "電話をかけて確認を…………あら？\r\n画面が真っ暗ですわ～。",
            "enText": "Call and check……… Oh my? The screen is dark!",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 230,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 193,
                    "pathId": -3724997662395620806
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6935200231056883952,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "充電器に接続し、ややあって息を吹き返したスマートフォンを\r\n確認してみると、留守番電話が何件か入っていた。",
            "enText": "After plugging in the charger, I checked my smartphone, \nwhich had somewhat reluctantly come to life, and found \nthat it had several answering machines.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": -6029528542480604067
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8375907035946710815,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロ家の運転手",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『ブライトお嬢様、失礼いたします。本日の予定に関してですが、\r\n諸事情ございまして延期の運びとなりました』",
            "enText": "Miss Bright, excuse me. We have had to postpone today's \nappointment for a number of reasons.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 283,
            "pathId": 1731165891621231736,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロ家の運転手",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "『つきましては、恐縮ではございますが\r\n学園からの外出も不要となりますので――』",
            "enText": "As for the \"I'm sorry, but there is no \nneed for you to leave the academy.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 187,
            "pathId": -1056960667213138663,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "……まあ、3時間も前のメッセージなのですね。\r\nということは……。",
            "enText": "…… Well, the message is 3 hours old. So it is ……",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 251,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": -7929703613981697164
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 2402440641770772941
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1951409154239255233,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "もしかして、トレーナーさまにも\r\nずいぶん待ちぼうけをさせてしまいましたでしょうか～。",
            "enText": "I hope I didn't make your trainer wait too long.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 192,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -7369184340471461541
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 151,
                    "pathId": -5452933570326142752
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2127287321931810510,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "おかげで明日の分も仕事を進めることができたし、\r\n自分も止めなかったのだから気にしていないと伝えた。すると――",
            "enText": "I told her I didn't care because it allowed me to go ahead with \nmy work for tomorrow and I didn't stop myself. Then―",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 116,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": 574758121384493260
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 154,
                    "pathId": 3593422516264597404
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8604212991569583136,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "であれば、よいのですけれど～……\r\nちょっぴり、『のんびり』しすぎた気もいたしますわ。",
            "enText": "I hope so, but…… I feel a little too \"laid-back\".",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 210,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 189,
                    "pathId": -6189891009927451529
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 4694280511478999482
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8055250135786995248,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "わたくしは、\r\nたくさんお話ができて楽しかったのですけれど～……。",
            "enText": "I had a lot of fun talking with them - ……",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 171,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "俺も楽しかったぞ",
                    "enText": "I had a good time, too.",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "私も楽しかったよ",
                    "enText": "I had a great time too.",
                    "nextBlock": 30
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 131,
                    "pathId": -2877528927244415815
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3690475863687425131,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "うふふ、そうですか？　なら、よかったのかしら。",
            "enText": "Uh-huh, is that so? Then I guess it was good.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 189,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 201,
                    "pathId": 5836426198464927480
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": -6042606087998354676
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5621502755436644443,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロブライト",
            "enName": "Mejiro Bright",
            "jpText": "……よかったのかしら？",
            "enText": "I wonder if…… was a good idea?",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 59,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -8738119691587775455
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": 1703057621127637822
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4689170770134917063,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "すっかり日は傾いてしまったものの……\r\nゆっくり充実した時間を過ごせたことには違いない。",
            "enText": "Although the sun had completely set…… it must have been a slow \nand fulfilling time.",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": -2420394761767038974
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": -1440821812548080770
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3419366756540422664,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "何やら不思議そうな顔をしたメジロブライトを寮まで送り、\r\nその日は仕事を終えることにした。",
            "enText": "I dropped her off at her dormitory with a curious look on her \nface, and finished my work for the day.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "pathId": -1604941937993399034,
            "blockIdx": 33
        }
    ],
    "modified": 1657429823
}